description:
Get the the top the fun way. Built for big days of literally hanging out, these are the ultimate pants for full days of climbing. They tick all the boxes for easy movement, lightness and durability.90-denier fabric is tough but light, with enough stretch for big moves.DWR coating sheds water.Flat elastic waistband sits comfortably under a harness or backpack.Articulated knees with slim tapering toward the ankles.2 front, 2 back drop-in and 1 zippered thigh pocket.Shock cord adjustment at the ankles.

